Is not my most typical Friday. I usually try to look nice, since i'm usually doing something that night... However, today is quite different. I layed in bed till 6:20 and finally after quite a prompting from my mother, somehow made my way to the kitchen for a poptart. The rest of the morning was a hazy zombie like trance. The only other thing I can recall is that i had five more minutes until I had to start walking to the bus stop. I looked in the mirror and after a few seconds just said "**** it". Tonight is a special night:: yeah this is my theme song today
